cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

The paper deals with image classification and pattern recognition, which are core topics in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of different families of descriptors for feature extraction and classification also suggests that the paper could belong to the information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper deals with real-world images and datasets, which could also make it relevant to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
